{"tid":2396592,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人離開，我好痛苦","createTime":"2021-02-05T17:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T08:36:09.000Z","uid":45772,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a244eed6587822114baeeae00e1d3d6828e20f31","tid":2396592,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"二十幾年一齊相處，由細照顧我到大，日日都見面傾計，相處時間仲多過同老豆老母<br />\n<br />\n我真係好愛你，我好唔習慣冇咗你<br />\n你走得真係好突然。<br />\n我實在太多遺憾，好多野冇機會同你講，好多野冇機會同你一齊去完成<br />\n對唔住，我愛你<br />\n可唔可以報夢比我？ 我想同你道別"},{"pid":"772d0941d6324011fd778255db6dae62e093744b","tid":2396592,"uid":208323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e8ecf390a9ba87462a0529cb92ba8c2d6af71d","tid":2396592,"uid":45772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"我有時要好早五點幾起身出門口，你會較鬧鐘四點幾起身之後預備埋早餐先叫醒我"},{"pid":"7431fc3a6ab9379ab9619f8008b0b90186f17b6e","tid":2396592,"uid":45772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:07:30.000Z","msg":"每次我返到屋企，無論你響梳化做緊乜都好，都會擰轉頭望門口； 如果見到係我嘅話你會好開心，問我去咗邊度。 我好鍾意呢種有人期待自己嘅感覺。"},{"pid":"4cf3d1a84e526181eea12203af4c02d5baff7c20","tid":2396592,"uid":375414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306fdcc80318d661349b0d172d4405b49ca68ac9","tid":2396592,"uid":10712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:08:20.000Z","msg":"果種痛我明<br />\n我經歷左幾次 睇化左 ........................................"},{"pid":"9776593692563511ca8c909c15bf4e150a7a6bfb","tid":2396592,"uid":375414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:08:33.000Z","msg":"🙏🏻RIP"},{"pid":"c84dfc49040cb53c5ccf4151e3b14717f769feab","tid":2396592,"uid":22969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:08:51.000Z","msg":"係咪啊爺啊嫲嗰啲？喊出嚟舒服啲 <br />\n旁人都幫唔到你太多 <br />\n只能靠自己捱過最辛苦既呢段時間 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db642418e55e615737e9dc0ef5613845f6868833","tid":2396592,"uid":321227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"保重"},{"pid":"63945cdeedc70d519622cc2da11598d9289da3e7","tid":2396592,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:09:25.000Z","msg":"你最近成日叫我帶你出去行吓，我都唔知係自己懶，定驚你感染武肺，所以都冇帶你出去行。 對唔住。"},{"pid":"8868bdc089236dca0eb27707c8f6be41d108f1dd","tid":2396592,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:11:12.000Z","msg":"你臨出門口之前，催我去剪頭髮，我仲講啲好難聽嘅說話鬧你。 係我衰，係我唔好，對唔住。 我永遠都會愛你。"},{"pid":"30afab3b79a24b11a041185888cc1e6d0ffdc3f1","tid":2396592,"uid":385428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:17:04.000Z","msg":"人係有靈魂㗎 佢會聽到你嘅心底話&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"04c42bfd5b29ff3757c2a40cbe1e4fcf3e061acf","tid":2396592,"uid":176860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:28:05.000Z","msg":"我都好掛住我嫲嫲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507beec330a1a006233d020697d4d36f330d3a07","tid":2396592,"uid":228679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:28:33.000Z","msg":"對仲在世嘅人好啲<br />\n唔好令自己有下一個遺憾"},{"pid":"ce3a0f570b2e163a89d69211674785453bffd607","tid":2396592,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167054dcb0826c3f7fefefc94dfe3df859e3d80f","tid":2396592,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T17:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009bf23018495c403c276a762eb21ccf